      "message": "Thanks for the advice.\n\nIn task like https://chromium-swarm.appspot.com/task?d\u003dtrue\u0026id\u003d4d1b73d8901d9210 I found tags like \"device_os:L\" and \"device_os_type:userdebug\" and \"device_type:hammerhead\".\n\nShould we also add \"device_os_type\"? Or that tag doesn\u0027t matter?",
